summary: Well good evening Sydney and welcome to the reputation Stadium Tour! First things first, I want to say thank you to my...
text: Well good evening Sydney and welcome to the reputation Stadium Tour! First things first, I want to say thank you to my incredible tour mates on this tour. How much did you love the unforgettable Broods tonight? How much did you love the fantastic Charli XCX tonight? Alright guys, we have come here today on a Friday night in Sydney, and I’m playing a lot of songs from an album that I made called reputation. On this particular album there are a lot of themes explored that we will get into as the night goes on. But for now, I want to talk to you very briefly about right now is the concept of real friends. You know what they say about real friends, right? They’re the ones that will show up for you in rain or shine, isn’t that right Sydney? You have showed up, your'e screaming the words to every single song, you are dancing, you are bouncing, you have your hands in the air, I could not possibly love you more than I do at this moment right now. And it is beautiful Sydney! I’d even say it’s above beautiful…is there a word to describe something that’s more than beautiful?
source: Taylor before Gorgeous in Sydney on November 2nd
